{
    "title": "Codinome Beija-flor",
    "artist": "Luiz Melodia",
    "composer": "Cazuza / Ezequiel Neves / Reinaldo Arias",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7M\">A7M</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7M\">A7M</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Pra que mentir, fingir que perdoou</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7M\">D7M</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E/D\">E/D</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Tentar ficar amigos sem rancor</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7M\">D7M</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E/D\">E/D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">A emoção acabou</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7M\">D7M</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E/D\">E/D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que coincidência é o amor</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7\">Bm7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#m7\">C#m7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7M\">D7M</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/E\">D/E</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F/G\">F/G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">A nossa música nunca mais tocou</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7M\">A7M</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7M\">A7M</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Pra que usar de tanta educação</span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7M\">D7M</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E/D\">E/D</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Pra destilar terceiras intenções</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7M\">D7M</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E/D\">E/D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Desperdiçando o meu mel</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7M\">D7M</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E/D\">E/D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Devagarzinho flor em flor</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7\">Bm7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#m7\">C#m7</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7M\">D7M</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/E\">D/E</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F/G\">F/G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Entre os meus inimigos, Beija-Flor</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu protegi seu nome por amor</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7M\">F7M</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Em um codinome Beija-Flor</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7(4)\">E7(4)</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não responda nunca meu amor</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7M\">F7M</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Pra qualquer um na rua Beija-Flor</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7M\">F7M</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que só eu que podia</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7M\">F7M</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Dentro da tua orelha fria</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7M\">F7M</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Dizer segredos de liquidificador</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7M\">F7M</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Você sonhava acordada</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7M\">F7M</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Um jeito de não sentir dor</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7M\">F7M</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Prendia o choro e aguava o bom do amor</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7M\">F7M</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A9\">A9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Prendia o choro e aguava o bom do amor</span>\n",
